{"tid":1359153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位download 一個反恐App","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:06:45.000Z","uid":16184,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e1380436c18241c609846517db581512d360e1","tid":1359153,"uid":16184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"SG secure <br />\n一個由新加坡政府出既反恐app，主要係教導大家遇到恐怖襲擊時應該要點做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFA6umj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFA6umj.png&h=7e830aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple store/ Google play 都可以下載<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPXQbzS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPXQbzS.png&h=16114ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有個位可以直接報驚，按999都係報狗，但相信唔會用到， 因為狗係唔會理我地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VoRtHGZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVoRtHGZ.png&h=b3aa10f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係呢part</span></span>， 按入去會有教學，萬一發生恐襲應該點做，期中包括721既地鐵場景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qByPr9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqByPr9c.png&h=6d852820&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQDzDfT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQDzDfT.png&h=c8739fc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhbtHHz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhbtHHz.png&h=2d77c11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面有幾條片比大家睇，睇晒佢大約15分中左右，亦有互動環節，確保大家明白要點樣面對<br />\n<br />\n最後一個chapter會教大家如何安慰恐襲後既朋友同社會<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！ </span>"},{"pid":"d2c8b04e6ae605f5fb152b941534bec6640e319a","tid":1359153,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"9cb148f6a25a0bd2afd34b76